data.description: Discover the epitome of privacy & equity in this serene rambler set on 4.5 acres w/ tranquil stream. Ideal for mechanics, woodworkers, car collectors, two spacious shops, ample parking, and is fenced for horses or cows, offering room for expansion. This cherished 4-bedroom home has been lovingly maintained for over 30 years waiting someone to continue its legacy. The residence boasts a large open kitchen with an antique stove, eat-in kitchen, spacious living room flooded w/ natural light from the large windows, covered deck. remote awning, fire pit, propane fireplace. The primary room is truly massive w/ walk in closet. Priced under value, this listing offers a unique opportunity for you to remodel and personalize it to match your vision.
